OL,4,Ccat banned from Costa cafe
OL,6,FWhile people regularly mistake him as
OL,7,Fbeing lost, he's not actually far from
OL,8,Fhome and loves to frequent the car
OL,9,Fparks looking for attention and even
OL,10,Fvisits the Tesco Express store, where
OL,11,Fhe sometimes gets fed.
OL,13,FOne regular, Lilith Hodgson, was so
OL,14,Fhorrified by the decision that she set
OL,15,Fup a petition to demand that Costa
OL,16,Fallow Dillon back in.
OL,18,FShe said that Dillon's presence had
OL,19,Fbeen "a highlight throughout (her)
OL,20,Flife" and she hoped that Costa would
OL,21,Freconsider the decision.
