OL,6,FShe wrote: "I write this, deeply moved
OL,7,Fby the story of Dillon, the local cat
OL,8,Fthat has become part of the fabric of
OL,9,Four local community in its daily
OL,10,Fpresence at Costa.
OL,12,F"Dillon's companionship has been a
OL,13,Fhighlight throughout my life and
OL,14,Fundoubtedly the lives of many others.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
