OL,4,Ccat banned from Costa cafe
OL,6,F"We are encouraging local support in
OL,7,Fproviding a voice for Dillon, and the
OL,8,Fcommunity's desire to see him returned
OL,9,Fto his favourite lounging spot inside
OL,10,FCosta.
OL,12,F"Please sign this petition to bring
OL,13,FDillon back where he belongs. We
OL,14,Fbelieve that an exception can be made
OL,15,Ffor Dillon, and Costa can once again
OL,16,Fbe a haven where residents and this
OL,17,Fremarkable cat can come together in
OL,18,Fmutual respect and admiration.
