OL,6,F"Let's stand together ` for Dillon,
OL,7,Ffor our community, for companionship
OL,8,Fat Costa. Please sign this petition."
OL,10,FDespite the petition, Costa Coffee
OL,11,Fconfirmed that the feline will not be
OL,12,Fallowed back indoors.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the coffee giant said:
OL,15,F"Dillon the cat has been a well-loved
OL,16,Fvisitor to our franchise owned and
OL,17,Foperated store in Pentewan Park.
