OL,6,F"However, in line with our policy,
OL,7,Fonly assistance animals and well-
OL,8,Fbehaved dogs (in our dog-friendly
OL,9,Fstores) are permitted in our stores.
OL,11,F"We appreciate the community's
OL,12,Funderstanding as we uphold a
OL,13,Fconsistent experience for all
OL,14,Fcustomers."
